title: Deep Purple - Live at Budokan (Deluxe 2-CD) 2016 ak320
description:
Deep Purple - Live at Budokan (Deluxe 2-CD) 2016 ak320

Deep Purple kicked off their 2016 tour with a series of shows in historical venues around Japan, including Tokyo's Nippon Budokan. According to Mike Airey, keyboard tech for Deep Purple, the show at the Budokan was sold out.
Which was no surprise to me, the band is legendary here in the land of the rising sun. They have played some of their finest shows there. (both there's in one sentence).
This is also a Analogkid bonus Hall of  Fame Edition
